UBA Online Account:
Bank Everywhere

The UBA Online Account is a unique account designed for people who desire to carry out their banking activities purely online, without visiting a bank branch. Enjoy the flexibility of banking on the go with our electronic channels (internet banking, mobile banking, ATM and EmailMoni) and get a 30% concession on transaction fee.
